OL,3,C'It feels all wrong to me': Former Co-
OL,4,Cop director slams proposed changes
OL,6,FThe former president of the Co-op in
OL,7,Fthe Channel Islands has voiced his
OL,8,Fconcerns about proposed changes to the
OL,9,FCo-Operative Society.
OL,11,FDeputy Peter Roffey is against new
OL,12,Fproposals to change how directors in
OL,13,Fthe islands are chosen.
OL,15,FHe told ITV News "At the moment you
OL,16,Fhave to have spend an average of #25
OL,17,Fat the Co-op a week in order to be a
OL,18,Fdirector, the proposal is to take it
OL,19,Fdown below #10 a week.
