OL,3,C'It feels all wrong to me': Former Co-
OL,4,Cop director slams proposed changes
OL,6,F"You can have somebody that hardly
OL,7,Fever shops at the Co-op being a
OL,8,Fdirector. That just feels all wrong to
OL,9,Fme, it's supposed to be controlled by
OL,10,Fits members, by its customers", he
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FIn response the Channel Islands' Co-op
OL,14,Fsaid: "We're proposing these changes
OL,15,Fto fine tune our governance and ensure
OL,16,Four board is ready to tackle future
OL,17,Fchallenges.
